    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1925-05-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1925-05-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="404"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d404">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.129/69 F. W.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chief of the Division of Mexican Affairs</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gunther</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Assistant Solicitor</hi> (<persName
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Vallance</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-05-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 1, 1925</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Mr. Vallance</hi>: Mr. de Negri, First Secretary of
                    the Mexican Embassy, has just called on me and stated that his Ambassador was
                    instructed by telegraph by the Mexican Foreign Office to procure from us the
                    proposed agenda of the Conference on May 15, showing in full just what subjects
                    will be touched upon. I told him that the Mexican Foreign Office had been
                    informed through Mr. Sheffield of every new development in the matter of this
                    Conference, but that I would endeavor to supply him with additional data.</p>
                <p>Can you supply me with the information?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>F[<hi rend="smallcaps">ranklin</hi>] M. G[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                            >unther</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
